]] (Companies A, B, D, E, F and G, 1st Battalion and Companies F and G, 2nd Battalion): Maj Grotius R. Giddings\n|-\n| 2nd Brigade\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\nCol [[Sidney Burbank]]\n|\n* [[2nd Infantry Regiment (United States)|2nd United States]] (Companies B, C, F, H, I and K): Maj [[Arthur Tracy Lee|Arthur T. Lee]] ('''w'''), Cpt Samuel A. McKee\n* [[7th Infantry Regiment (United States)|7th United States]] (Companies A, B, E and I): Cpt David P. Hancock\n* [[10th Infantry Regiment (United States)|10th United States]] (Companies D, G and H): Cpt William Clinton\n* [[11th Infantry Regiment (United States)|11th United States]] (Companies B, C, D, E, F and G): Maj [[DeLancey Floyd-Jones]]\n* [[17th Infantry Regiment (United States)|17th United States]] (Companies A, C, D, G and H, 1st Battalion and Companies A and B, 2nd Battalion): Ltc [[James Durrell Greene|James D. Greene]]\n|-\n| 3rd Brigade\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\nBG [[Stephen H. Weed]] ('''k''')\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\nCol [[Kenner Garrard]]\n|\n* [[140th New York]]: Col [[Patrick O'Rorke]] ('''k'''), Ltc Louis Ernst, Maj Isaiah Force\n* [[146th New York Volunteer Infantry Regiment|146th New York]]: Col [[Kenner Garrard]], Ltc David T. Jenkins\n* [[91st Pennsylvania Infantry|91st Pennsylvania]]: Ltc Joseph H. Sinex\n* [[155th Pennsylvania Infantry|155th Pennsylvania]]: Ltc John H. Cain\n|-\n| rowspan=2 |\n[[Pennsylvania Reserves|Third Division]] <ref>joined corps June 28. The Second Brigade left in the Department of Washington</ref>\n\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\nBG [[Samuel W. Crawford]]\n| 1st Brigade\n<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\nCol [[William McCandless]]\n|\n* [[1st Pennsylvania Reserve Regiment|1st Pennsylvania Reserves]] (9 companies): Col William C. Talley ('''w''')\n* [[2nd Pennsylvania Reserve Regiment|2nd Pennsylvania Reserves]]: Ltc George A. Woodward\n* [[6th Pennsylvania Reserve Regiment|6th Pennsylvania Reserves]]: Ltc Wellington H. Ent\n* [[13th Pennsylvania Reserve Regiment|13th Pennsylvania Reserves]]: Col Charles F. Ta